# Note about ANSI colors:
# Ghostty handles ANSI colors automatically. The color0-15 format from Alacritty
# is not supported. Ghostty will use the terminal's default color scheme or
# any specified theme. For full Dracula ANSI colors, you may need to:
# 1. Use a Ghostty theme file if available
# 2. Let Ghostty use system default colors
# 3. Configure colors in your shell prompt/theme instead

